<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/427880-can-a-married-man-write-a-book-like-this">Can a married man write a book like this and continue to live peacefully with his wife? I picture Murakami&#39;s wife rolling up the manuscript, slapping him across the face with it and shrieking, &quot;Why don&#39;t you go ask whoever you&#39;re really in love with what she thinks about this book?&quot;</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_427880'><a id="like_count_community_question_427880" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/427880?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">58 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F17799.South_of_the_Border_West_of_the_Sun">like</a></span>

